{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn3.am730.com.hk/processed/2026-05/1028291/block/singleImage/3073130/df/01KQPCXB6DQGZVSJ7QABJ43C1V.png?updatedAt=1777794518\" alt=\"Dss 0\">\n    <p>澳門4月博彩收入升5.5%。</p>\n    <img src=\"/assets/v2/img/ui/amlogo_grey_600_500.png\" alt=\"adblk4\">\n    <p>澳門博彩監察協調局公布，4月博彩收入198.94億澳門元，按年升5.5%。首4個月累計博彩收入857.67億澳門元，按年升12.1%。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T08:32:53.742404+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":82,"images":2,"source":"am730","fallback":"none"}}